  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627240/extras/4504e51f1302848bb0a9a6a7a4e0de45.avif?t=1696715610\" width=610 height=235 /></span><br>The stove can go if there are wheels and firewood!<br>You have to control a crazy stove and run away from a dangerous saw. And why did the stove have wheels, there is no answer for sure, but maybe the pike wanted it that way<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627240/extras/1df601c7f8b63a3c8d389714dcc8b2c1.poster.avif?t=1696715610\" width=594 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627240/extras/1df601c7f8b63a3c8d389714dcc8b2c1.webm?t=1696715610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627240/extras/1df601c7f8b63a3c8d389714dcc8b2c1.mp4?t=1696715610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features of the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rhythm-based Action Platforming!<br></li><li>Many achievements.<br></li><li>Oven with wheels in the winter forest.<br></li><li>The furnace runs away from the saw.<br></li><li>The oven smokes a lot.<br></li><li>It's snowing in the woods.<br></li><li>The biggest danger is the saws.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Management: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The oven goes automatically. <br></li><li>You can accelerate the movement by moving forward. <br></li><li>You can jump and slow down in front of obstacles.</li></ul>",
